    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Wood of trees belonging to the genus Robinia, ranging in color from yellow with a greenish tint to medium golden-brown, and used for making wheel spokes, ladder rungs, and occasionally furniture.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
